---
// VisionMision.astro
---

<section class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div
    class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="absolute -bottom-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-surface-200 rounded-full blur-3xl"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto md:px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12 lg:gap-20">
      <div
        class="group p-10 md:p-16 md:rounded-3xl bg-surface-100 border-y md:border border-base-light hover:border-primary/20 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/10 transition-all duration-500 h-fit"
      >
        <div
          class="mb-8 w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-8 h-8"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-ink-base mb-6 italic font-serif">
          Nuestra Misión
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
          Brindar atención dermatológica de <strong>alta especialización</strong
          >, combinando el rigor científico de la escuela médica peruana con las
          tecnologías láser más avanzadas del mundo, para restaurar no solo la
          salud de la piel, sino la seguridad de cada paciente.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-8 space-y-3">
          <li
            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-ink-muted font-medium"
          >
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
            Ética médica innegociable.
          </li>
          <li
            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-ink-muted font-medium"
          >
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
            Actualización académica constante.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div
        class="group p-10 md:p-16 md:rounded-3xl bg-ink-base text-white hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/20 transition-all duration-500 md:mt-12"
      >
        <div
          class="mb-8 w-16 h-16 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-500"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-8 h-8"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 italic font-serif">
          Nuestra Visión
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          Ser reconocidos como el centro dermatológico de referencia en Lima,
          distinguiéndonos por la <strong
            >naturalidad de nuestros resultados</strong
          > estéticos y la precisión diagnóstica clínica, liderando el camino hacia
          una dermatología más humana y tecnológica.
        </p>
        <div
          class="mt-10 pt-10 border-t border-white/10 flex items-center justify-between"
        >
          <span
            class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold text-primary"
            >Proyección 2030</span
          >
          <div class="flex -space-x-3">
            <div
              class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-ink-base bg-surface-300"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-ink-base bg-primary"
            >
            </div>
            <div
              class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-ink-base bg-primary-light"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
